French Business Confidence Falls From Near Three-Year High

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-02-18T07:50:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/french-business-confidence-falls-from-near-three-year-high.html
French business confidence fell in 
February for the first time in three months on signs domestic 
demand is slowing.    France 's Business Sentiment Indicator dropped
to 106 from 108, the Insee said today in an e-mailed
statement. Economists expected a reading of 109, according to
the median of 12 estimates gathered by Bloomberg News.  The last time the index declined was in November. For  To contact the reporter on this story:
